- QEEG (Quantitative EEG) processing capabilities
- PDF generation features
- Supabase integration
- Patient management functionality
- Algorithm processing for neurological data

The project is on the `main` branch with several modified files and many untracked documentation files related to PDF generation fixes, Supabase migration, and various troubleshooting guides.
